Add domDecay transfer for _aboveGroundVeryFastSoil, _belowGroundVeryFastSoil, _aboveGroundFastSoil, _belowGroundFastSoil, _mediumSoil, _softwoodStemSnag, _softwoodBranchSnag, _hardwoodStemSnag, _hardwoodBranchSnag.
